like a streetcar.

56:43.964 --> 56:45.964
MAYNARD BARNES: The perpetrators
will be quickly put down.

56:46.172 --> 56:47.798
Justice for Charlie Dodson!

56:47.964 --> 56:51.047
♪ Wade in the water ♪

56:51.673 --> 56:54.047
Mr. Mason's evidence
is coming up short.

56:54.339 --> 56:56.089
You're pulling this out
of your ass, boy-o.

56:56.172 --> 56:57.464
Oh, that I agree with.

56:57.547 --> 56:59.631
The cops barely investigated
the case.

56:59.714 --> 57:02.964
-I'm the lawyer here!
-Then act like one, goddammit!

57:03.339 --> 57:04.631
This case is getting to you.

57:04.964 --> 57:07.464
You're a detective,
did I hear wrong, Mr. Mason?

57:09.130 --> 57:12.047
You guys are breaking
so many laws right now.

57:12.881 --> 57:14.798
♪ (MUSIC INTENSIFIES) ♪

57:16.047 --> 57:19.297
-This is over!
-I'm not done yet!

57:20.923 --> 57:22.172
MAN: The hell are you
doing here?

